440
00:25:36,260 --> 00:25:38,860
Sometimes, she loses her temper
and breaks things.

441
00:25:39,540 --> 00:25:40,340
Mrs. Su,

442
00:25:40,900 --> 00:25:42,620
you've been having hard days.

443
00:25:44,260 --> 00:25:45,020
How about this?

444
00:25:45,980 --> 00:25:49,020
I can arrange for Ms. Su
to go to a sanatorium.

445
00:25:49,380 --> 00:25:50,180
In this way,

446
00:25:51,180 --> 00:25:52,180
you won't be too exhausted.

447
00:25:52,180 --> 00:25:53,620
You can get rid of some burdens, too.

448
00:25:53,900 --> 00:25:56,900
No need. I've retired.

449
00:25:56,980 --> 00:25:58,740
I don't have things to do at home.

450
00:25:59,180 --> 00:26:00,740
I can take care of her.

451
00:26:00,820 --> 00:26:01,620
Mrs. Su,

452
00:26:02,100 --> 00:26:04,380
