466
00:26:29,660 --> 00:26:31,100
Don't worry about it.

467
00:26:32,100 --> 00:26:33,380
That'd be great.

468
00:26:36,020 --> 00:26:37,100
But, well,

469
00:26:37,100 --> 00:26:39,180
