567
00:31:49,060 --> 00:31:50,140
The point is, I won't stress out.

568
00:31:50,500 --> 00:31:51,260
Why?

569
00:31:51,340 --> 00:31:52,460
Why a deliveryman

570
00:31:52,460 --> 00:31:53,500
instead of a doctor?

571
00:31:55,260 --> 00:31:56,020
Nothing.

572
00:32:00,380 --> 00:32:01,900
You'll be the surgeon tomorrow, right?

573
00:32:08,500 --> 00:32:09,820
Yes, as scheduled.

574
00:32:10,700 --> 00:32:11,940
But I may not be needed.

575
00:32:12,380 --> 00:32:13,900
After all, my hospital has

576
00:32:13,900 --> 00:32:14,620
many great doctors.

577
00:32:21,460 --> 00:32:22,100
Come on.

578
00:32:22,460 --> 00:32:23,780
Let me take you somewhere.

579
00:32:25,500 --> 00:32:26,500
Where are we going, Jiang?

580
00:32:31,820 --> 00:32:33,060
When did you learn jujitsu?

581
00:32:33,260 --> 00:32:34,140
How come I didn't know?

582
00:32:34,140 --> 00:32:36,260
Last time,
Dr. Li did jujitsu in the bar,

583
00:32:38,620 --> 00:32:39,820
