584
00:32:41,140 --> 00:32:42,300
Then, I learned some.

585
00:32:42,860 --> 00:32:43,620
Against sexual harassment.

586
00:32:44,620 --> 00:32:45,500
Harassment?

587
00:32:46,260 --> 00:32:47,380
I'm your boyfriend,

588
00:32:47,700 --> 00:32:48,900
not a pervert.

589
00:32:49,580 --> 00:32:50,460
Fang Mingfan,

590
00:32:50,860 --> 00:32:52,620
now take me as the demon in your heart.

591
00:32:52,700 --> 00:32:53,700
Either I will defeat you,

592
00:32:53,700 --> 00:32:54,900
