602
00:33:21,260 --> 00:33:22,140
Mercy, Jiang.

603
00:33:22,740 --> 00:33:23,140
Mercy.

604
00:33:23,380 --> 00:33:24,140
What have I done?

605
00:33:24,140 --> 00:33:25,260
