617
00:33:44,140 --> 00:33:45,660
I'm not a coward!

618
00:33:47,500 --> 00:33:48,540
I'm not!

619
00:34:01,500 --> 00:34:02,300
Fang Mingfan,

620
00:34:03,380 --> 00:34:04,900
