635
00:35:28,140 --> 00:35:29,020
Trust yourself.

636
00:35:29,540 --> 00:35:30,620
You're going to be fine.

637
00:35:31,020 --> 00:35:33,140
Boss, be my first assistant.

638
00:35:34,780 --> 00:35:35,620
If anything happens,

639
00:35:35,620 --> 00:35:36,740
