& Operating Room]

648
00:36:04,900 --> 00:36:06,620
Boss, are you coming in?

649
00:36:07,020 --> 00:36:08,020
No.

650
00:36:08,380 --> 00:36:09,380
I just came to have a look.

651
00:36:09,380 --> 00:36:10,140
Dr. Gu,

652
00:36:11,020 --> 00:36:12,780
if you can't stop worrying,

653
00:36:13,140 --> 00:36:14,300
