700
00:38:10,620 --> 00:38:11,260
OK.

701
00:38:14,740 --> 00:38:16,020
I left my phone in my office

702
00:38:16,020 --> 00:38:16,860
instead of taking it.

703
00:38:16,860 --> 00:38:18,260
Would you like to use mine?

704
00:38:18,260 --> 00:38:19,620
No, thanks. I'll use the landline

705
00:38:19,620 --> 00:38:20,980
and call the office first.

706
00:38:21,100 --> 00:38:21,900
OK.

707
00:38:38,100 --> 00:38:38,900
Dr. Gu,

708
00:38:40,020 --> 00:38:40,860
in the whole building,

709
00:38:40,860 --> 00:38:42,260
you're the only neurosurgery expert.

710
00:38:42,260 --> 00:38:43,900
The E.N.T. Department just requested

711
00:38:43,900 --> 00:38:45,300
a joint consultation
with the respiratory

712
00:38:45,300 --> 00:38:46,740
and neurosurgery departments.

713
00:38:46,740 --> 00:38:47,860
OK. I'm on my way.

714
00:38:47,860 --> 00:38:48,500
All right.

715
00:39:21,060 --> 00:39:23,660
[In Operation]

716
00:39:32,220 --> 00:39:34,020
Doctor, how's my daughter?

717
00:39:34,380 --> 00:39:35,500
The operation was successful.

718
00:39:36,380 --> 00:39:38,100
She'll be under observation in the ICU

719
00:39:38,380 --> 00:39:40,020
