00:40:17,380 --> 00:40:18,140
Very successful.

737
00:40:18,770 --> 00:40:20,770
I knew you would make it.

738
00:40:22,100 --> 00:40:22,890
You're awesome.

739
00:40:27,660 --> 00:40:28,500
Jiang,

740
00:40:28,900 --> 00:40:30,340
