762
00:41:17,780 --> 00:41:18,900
No one can get out.

763
00:41:19,020 --> 00:41:20,020
Pneumonic pestis?

764
00:41:21,260 --> 00:41:22,660
That's a Class A infectious disease.

765
00:41:22,980 --> 00:41:24,660
Whoever is infected may die.

766
00:41:25,140 --> 00:41:26,020
Throughout the building,

767
00:41:26,020 --> 00:41:28,260
