792
00:42:41,820 --> 00:42:42,700
I have a plane to catch.

793
00:42:42,700 --> 00:42:43,700
In such a hurry?

794
00:42:47,540 --> 00:42:48,780
Be careful.

795
00:42:48,780 --> 00:42:49,420
Mom.

796
00:42:49,980 --> 00:42:51,540
Avoid crowded areas for now,

797
00:42:51,540 --> 00:42:52,820
